frames.caption: A humanoid wolf figure stands on a snowy mountain peak, draped in a blue cloak with fur trim. It holds a lantern on a staff, casting a warm glow against the cold, twilight backdrop of snow-covered hills.
frames.description: The scene depicts a mystical, fantasy setting at dusk or dawn, with a humanoid wolf character standing on a snowy mountaintop. The warm light from the lantern contrasts with the cool tones of the snow and sky, creating an enchanting atmosphere.

frames.caption: A lone figure draped in a blue cloak stands on a snowy cliff, holding a lantern that casts a warm glow. The backdrop features expansive snow-covered mountains under a vibrant sunset sky. The scene evokes a sense of solitude and contemplation amidst the vast wilderness.
frames.description: The scene is set in a mountainous, snow-covered landscape during sunset. A solitary figure, possibly a traveler or a mystical character, is standing on a cliff edge, holding a lantern. The setting sun paints the sky in hues of orange and pink, contrasting with the cold, blue tones of the snow.
